==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Forespeak
<hw>Fore*speak"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To foretell; to
predict.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My mother was half a witch; never anything that she
<qex>forespake</qex> but came to pass.</q> <rj><qau>Beau. &
Fl.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forespeaking</ent>⟦br⟧
